  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-01 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This synthetic adversarial package embeds an orphan Claim (W-EP-01): the central credibility claim is richly described and referenced via bindsClaim but carries no prov:wasDerivedFrom link to any Evidence node. ValidationResults are fully provenance-chained to Evidence; the Claim itself is not.",
