      "name": "Grid convergence index study — centrifugal pump CFD mesh",
      "description": "Three-level mesh refinement study (coarse: 2.1M cells, medium: 6.8M cells, fine: 18.4M cells). GCI computed per Celik et al. 2008 procedure. Apparent order of convergence p=1.87. GCI for NIH at design point: 3.2%. Oscillatory convergence not observed; monotonic convergence confirmed at all five operating points.",
      "prov:wasDerivedFrom": "https://doi.org/10.1115/1.2960953"
    }
