    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU2 (VAD hemolysis, Class III, MRL 5) is accepted for regulatory submission with documented gaps. Seven of thirteen credibility factors are formally assessed; all show achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5. Six factors remain not-assessed, representing epistemic gaps acknowledged in the submission. The central credibility claim (CFD-predicted NIH within clinical threshold with 18% margin at 95th percentile) is supported by three ValidationResults with full provenance to experimental bench data, Monte Carlo UQ outputs, and GCI study evidence. The credibility package is accepted as the basis for regulatory submission under 21 CFR 870.3545, with the understanding that post-market surveillance will address model form uncertainty and pulsatile flow equivalency gaps identified herein.",
    "decidedAt": "2026-04-19T00:00:00Z"
